{"tid":2413383,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"NVIDA出mining專用卡CMP , geforce 會限hash rate","createTime":"2021-02-18T15:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T06:42:49.000Z","uid":342823,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8d1abbf86e2b7cd9c48dbffe8e82983bb116c572","tid":2413383,"uid":342823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:54:15.000Z","msg":"geforce 好快大平買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/2021/02/18/geforce-cmp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.nvidia.com%2Fblog%2F2021%2F02%2F18%2Fgeforce-cmp%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69BPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=a5aa93ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/2021/02/18/geforce-cmp/</a>"},{"pid":"2d7fa6c6858138848c5fc95d1c18f83774f41b9e","tid":2413383,"uid":342823,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:55:32.000Z","msg":"We&rsquo;re limiting the hash rate of GeForce RTX 3060 GPUs so they&rsquo;re less desirable to miners and launching NVIDIA CMP for professional mining.<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Halving Hash Rate</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRTX 3060 software drivers are designed to detect specific attributes of the Ethereum cryptocurrency mining algorithm, and limit the hash rate, or cryptocurrency mining efficiency, by around 50 percent."},{"pid":"4047f937a686301922f1575ea9313ab7de36f0fb","tid":2413383,"uid":134415,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"買多一倍卡咪破解到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03fc880c5bbb27cfcbb9ccb817060f314a2935b","tid":2413383,"uid":146089,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,