kgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T16:11:23.000Z","msg":"衝業績專用產品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T16:15:32.000Z","msg":"粉飾下個招牌，你估nv係咩好人。<br />\n舊年8月幾我已經見到eth條chain幾日升左25%算力，屌我諗3080唔係9月先發售咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你再諗就知，佢地已經提早將d卡賣左比勇敢既礦工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"咁你好醒喎<br />\n有研究開blockchain? <br />\n<br />\n仲有冇咩insight 分享下"},{"pid":"9ef18419d97bad1254b24a262b4aae4bd9096325","tid":2413383,"uid":240069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"因為有傳大陸礦機商bitmain 會自己掘完一排堆尚未發售既機先再開賣俾客人 (陰謀論)<br />\n要推高ETH blockchain 算力25% 唔係細數, 真係似備貨而個timing 又係好夾9月頭個GeForce RTX 3000 發佈會"},{"pid":"d0fdea24e2aef08dfa637ed896923a087ceaa201","tid":2413383,"uid":240069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T17:28:14.000Z","msg":"睇返成個8月, 其實ETH network hash rate 都衹係穩步上升<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0gHtV5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0gHtV5.png&h=da9feb69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1 Sep 係RTX 3080 paper launch date<br />\n而17 Sep 係RTX 3080 hard launch date, 考慮返時差呢一日要出貨就即跌咗5% hash rate <br />\n參考個Ethereum Network Hash Rate Chart csv file 計返當日係少咗 9,451,935.30MH/s network hash rate, 而一張RTX 3080 86.54MH/s<br />\n即係發售當日少咗 109,220.42 近11萬張RTX 3080 既算力<br />\n當然亦有可能衹係各種coincidence 少咗呢堆算力而唔係有人unplug 咗11萬張卡出貨<br />\n<br />\nRef.: <a href=\"https://etherscan.io/chart/hashrate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetherscan.io%2Fchart%2Fhashrate&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69BPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=10da2a35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://etherscan.io/chart/hashrate</a>"},{"pid":"6976b3b8648b279b96bf464cfb02cf59d46aa0e5","tid":2413383,"uid":60695,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T17:45:11.000Z","msg":"算力受限嘅同時功耗都會因為硬件性能受限而下降<br />\n<br />\n一張卡一日堀到嘅錢少咗50%<br />\n但同時功耗都可能少咗40-50%<br />\n<br />\n真係掃多一倍卡就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且對礦佬嚟講買顯示卡掘其實係低成本租卡<br />\n<br />\nDriver/BIOS破解埋就回復現狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739d68c2fa73570c46a99f4c569aa798b50e894d","tid":2413383,"uid":135488,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:49:49.000Z","msg":"刀神黄狗點會唔知個driver會秒速畀贏國人破解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純粹做下樣畀班買唔到卡嘅gamers睇<br />\n<br />\n嗱我有做嘢架 順便衝一波業績<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfe47f5aa982d79f2242b77633602bc68898dff","tid":2413383,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T19:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ac63e1672ffe8df4a8b287d7814328398be121","tid":2413383,"uid":79510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T20:01:21.000Z","msg":"洗鬼破解,留住舊driver,掃晒現有型號就得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係打機淨係3060/3080ti可以買"},{"pid":"c3ff593e15002dbbd1447675b7a868a715e3240d","tid":2413383,"uid":146089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0fdea24e2aef08dfa637ed896923a087ceaa201","tid":2413383,"uid":240069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T17:28:14.000Z","msg":"睇返成個8月, 其實ETH network hash rate 都衹係穩步上升<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0gHtV5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0gHtV5.png&h=da9feb69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1 Sep 係RTX 3080 paper launch date<br />\n而17 Sep 係RTX 3080 hard launch date, 考慮返時差呢一日要出貨就即跌咗5% hash rate <br />\n參考個Ethereum Network Hash Rate Chart csv file 計返當日係少咗 9,451,935.30MH/s network hash rate, 而一張RTX 3080 86.54MH/s<br />\n即係發售當日少咗 109,220.42 近11萬張RTX 3080 既算力<br />\n當然亦有可能衹係各種coincidence 少咗呢堆算力而唔係有人unplug 咗11萬張卡出貨<br />\n<br />\nRef.: <a href=\"https://etherscan.io/chart/hashrate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetherscan.io%2Fchart%2Fhashrate&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69BPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=10da2a35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://etherscan.io/chart/hashrate</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T23:26:14.000Z","msg":"我係睇圖，8月1號開始呢d已經唔係穩步上升。<br />\n係大概1~2點鐘方向上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住我買左NV股票，提早佈局幾個月，d人總去炒AMD。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wJKqtJR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwJKqtJR.png&h=fd1394c3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}